net.opentsdb.rollup

类 RollupInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.rollup.RollupInterval

  • public class RollupInterval
extends Object
    Holds information about a rollup interval. During construction the inputs are validated.

        public boolean isDefaultInterval()
        Is it the default roll up interval that need to be written to default tsdb data table. So if true, which means the raw cell column qualifier is not encoded with the aggregate function and the cell might have been compacted
        返回:
        true if it is default rollup interval
